        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/rudi_finkler/{size}/710_2.png",
        "created_at": "2017-12-26T11:53:37.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Ian, from what I have tasted in the mid-price category over the last year and a half, I can recommend:</p>\n<p>2001, 2009 Le Moulin, 20% Cab. Franc<br>\n2004, 2012 Nenin, 20% Cab. Franc<br>\n2001, 2007 La Croix St. Georges, 5% Cab. Franc<br>\n2008 La Croix de Gay, 10% Cab. Franc<br>\n2000, 2001 La Pointe, 15% Cab. Franc<br>\n2000 Clos Ren\u00e9, 20% Cab. Franc<br>\n2006, 2009 La Petite Eglise, 15% Cab. Franc</p>",
