        "created_at": "2017-12-26T12:09:56.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Much appreciated Rudy.<br>\nI\u2019m hoping there will be some mature/semi/mature bottles there, but from recollection of the specific shop I know we\u2019ll be going to, there will be a decent smattering, but they\u2019re not specialists in mature wine\u2026 but do have an interesting selection and we\u2019re always happy to cellar the wine ourselves.</p>\n<p>Regards<br>\nIan</p>",
